t: "∆Åen (Malaa'ikaa…ìe) roondii…ìe Arsiki kin, e won…ìe bannge makki …ìen, hi…ìe subbunhinora yettugol Joomi ma…ì…ìe, …ìe gom…óina Mo, …ìe insinorana gom…óim…ìe …ìen (wiide): \"Joomi amen, A ya√±√±irii kala huunde, yurmeende e ganndal. Yawtan …ìen tuubu…ìe, …ìe jokki laawol Maa ngol, da…óndaa …ìe kadi lepte Dul…ìoowe ngen"